## Playwright test run: 12/12 passed

### Selector note (v1 -> v2 correction)

The original playwright-test.js used `button:has-text("Browse")` / `button:has-text("Provider")`
to find the CTA that navigates from the patient dashboard to the services page.
The backend seeds one appointment for the patient account (bk_001), so the dashboard renders
"Appointments (1)" and shows a "+ Book another appointment" button rather than "Browse providers".
Both CTAs trigger the same navigation; the v2 script accepts either label.

