## Hero flow verified step by step

1. Loaded https://michaelwegter.com/demos/healthstack-patient-portal/ -- title correct, React rendered.
2. Filled patient@healthstack.demo / DemoPatient123! -> clicked "Sign in securely".
3. API POST /healthstack/login returned 200 + JWT. Patient dashboard rendered ("My Dashboard",
   "Appointments (1)", seeded booking bk_001 shown with status CONFIRMED).
4. Clicked "+ Book another appointment" -- navigated to ServicesPage ("Find a Doctor").
5. API GET /healthstack/services returned 4 providers: Dr. Sarah Chen, Dr. Marcus Webb,
   Dr. Priya Nair, NP Jordan Kim.
6. Clicked "Book Appointment" on first provider -- slot picker rendered with AM/PM time slots.
7. Selected first available slot -> clicked "Confirm Appointment".
8. API POST /healthstack/book returned booking_id -> checkout page rendered with order summary.
9. Clicked "Pay $XX.00" -> API POST /healthstack/checkout returned pi_DEMO_... mock PaymentIntent.
10. Confirmation page showed green check + PaymentIntent ID.
11. Logged out -> logged in as admin@healthstack.demo / DemoAdmin123!.
12. Admin Dashboard loaded with stat cards, all-bookings table, audit log, and patient roster.

